Sentencas: Five Gd1-xSrxFe0.8Co0.2O3-delta. perovskites were synthesized using the glycine-nitrate process.
Titulo: Cone-Shaped Gd1-xSrxFe0.8Co0.2O3-δ Electrodes for SOFC Cathodes

Sentencas: The compounds were evaluated as solid oxide fuel cell cathodes using cone-shaped electrodes and electrochemical impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Cone-Shaped Gd1-xSrxFe0.8Co0.2O3-δ Electrodes for SOFC Cathodes

Sentencas: It was shown that the electrochemical activity depended on the amount of strontium in the perovskite; the main difference seemed to be whether the perovskite is a single or a two-phase compound.
Titulo: Cone-Shaped Gd1-xSrxFe0.8Co0.2O3-δ Electrodes for SOFC Cathodes

Sentencas: However, high-strontium-substituted Fe-Co-based perovskites have slightly higher performances than the low-strontium-substituted Fe-Co-based perovskites, as determined by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy on cone-shaped electrodes.
Titulo: Cone-Shaped Gd1-xSrxFe0.8Co0.2O3-δ Electrodes for SOFC Cathodes
